[2026-03-10T15:59:15Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01URhBnPVWnZj8gKvzrX6aFd","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Project Settings File: config.toml\n     2→\n     3→**Date:** 2026-03-06\n     4→**Status:** Design\n     5→\n     6→## Problem\n     7→\n     8→The per-project settings file is `.cloche/config` with no extension, making it\n     9→ambiguous and inconsistent with the TOML library in use.\n    10→\n    11→## Change\n    12→\n    13→Rename to `.cloche/config.toml`. No backwards compatibility with the old filename.\n    14→\n    15→## Default file (created by `cloche init`)\n    16→\n    17→```toml\n    18→# Cloche project configuration\n    19→\n    20→[orchestration]\n    21→enabled     = false\n    22→concurrency = 1\n    23→workflow    = \"develop\"\n    24→# tracker = \"beads\"\n    25→\n    26→[evolution]\n    27→enabled           = true\n    28→debounce_seconds  = 30\n    29→min_confidence    = \"medium\"\n    30→max_prompt_bullets = 50\n    31→```\n    32→\n    33→Notes:\n    34→- `orchestration.enabled` defaults to `false` so new projects don't start pulling tasks\n    35→  until explicitly opted in.\n    36→- All keys are present so the file is self-documenting.\n    37→- Commented-out keys (`tracker`) show optional overrides that rarely need changing.\n    38→\n    39→## Code changes\n    40→\n    41→| File | Change |\n    42→|------|--------|\n    43→| `internal/config/config.go` | `Load()`: change path from `\"config\"` to `\"config.toml\"` |\n    44→| `cmd/cloche/init.go` | Add `config.toml` to the files created by init |\n    45→| `.cloche/config` (existing file in this repo) | Rename to `.cloche/config.toml` |\n    46→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1833ddb6-4c99-47f1-b217-57b1c898f9f1","uuid":"993a3fda-6166-490c-b756-06fa7b7faf81","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-config-toml-design.md","content":"# Project Settings File: config.toml\n\n**Date:** 2026-03-06\n**Status:** Design\n\n## Problem\n\nThe per-project settings file is `.cloche/config` with no extension, making it\nambiguous and inconsistent with the TOML library in use.\n\n## Change\n\nRename to `.cloche/config.toml`. No backwards compatibility with the old filename.\n\n## Default file (created by `cloche init`)\n\n```toml\n# Cloche project configuration\n\n[orchestration]\nenabled     = false\nconcurrency = 1\nworkflow    = \"develop\"\n# tracker = \"beads\"\n\n[evolution]\nenabled           = true\ndebounce_seconds  = 30\nmin_confidence    = \"medium\"\nmax_prompt_bullets = 50\n```\n\nNotes:\n- `orchestration.enabled` defaults to `false` so new projects don't start pulling tasks\n  until explicitly opted in.\n- All keys are present so the file is self-documenting.\n- Commented-out keys (`tracker`) show optional overrides that rarely need changing.\n\n## Code changes\n\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `internal/config/config.go` | `Load()`: change path from `\"config\"` to `\"config.toml\"` |\n| `cmd/cloche/init.go` | Add `config.toml` to the files created by init |\n| `.cloche/config` (existing file in this repo) | Rename to `.cloche/config.toml` |\n","numLines":46,"startLine":1,"totalLines":46}}}
